Title: MediatR and MassTransit Going Commerical: What This Means For You
Description: Popular .NET libraries MediatR, AutoMapper, and MassTransit are transitioning to commercial licenses after over a decade of free open-source availability. This article examines the reasons behind these changes, what they mean for your projects, and the practical options available to developers moving forward.
